column2: SELECT a.specObjID, a.z, a.zErr, a.ra, a.dec, a.type, a.modelMag_u, a.modelMag_g, a.modelMag_r, a.modelMag_i, a.modelMag_z, a.modelMagErr_u, a.modelMagErr_g, a.modelMagErr_r, a.modelMagErr_i, a.modelMagErr_z, a.extinction_u, a.extinction_g, a.extinction_r, a.extinction_i, a.extinction_z, a.dered_u, a.dered_g, a.dered_r, a.dered_i, a.dered_z, b.specObjID, b.sfr_tot_p5#, b.specsfr_tot_p5#, b.lgm_tot_p5#, c.specObjID, c.spiral, c.elliptical, c.uncertain FROM SpecPhotoAll as a, galSpecExtra as b, zooSpec as c WHERE a.specObjID = b.specObjID and a.specObjID = c.specObjID and type = # and b.specsfr_tot_p5# > # ORDER BY a.specObjID OFFSET # ROWS FETCH NEXT # ROWS ONLY
